description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Lower Body + Core Circuit ' from the channel Rina Thomas.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Lower body adn core focus off Hydrow with dumbbells and 1-minute intervals on Hydrow.

Max rhythm: 24, Format: EMOM...
